/www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%91-Vi%C3%AAm-V%C5%A9/Tinh-v%E1%BB%87/poem-z2aR93ZRl7xZ55afJKxnMg">Tinh vệ - 精衛</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%91-Vi%C3%AAm-V%C5%A9/author-py5Vb_484Rgr_jQ_nkfQjw">Cố Viêm Vũ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%ABu-Vi%E1%BB%85n/%E1%BB%A8c-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-L%C6%B0-nh%E1%BB%8B-n%E1%BB%AF/poem-UUlvKpi0YJxC4BOTftjoUA">Ức Đồng Lư nhị nữ - 憶桐廬二女</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%ABu-Vi%E1%BB%85n/author-sRemHKkmYCdxkkHc58hcHA">Cừu Viễn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-Ch%E1%BA%A5p-T%C3%ADn/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-cung-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-EsrJ50N1LSoolas_uQYSdA">Xuất cung từ - 出宮詞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-Ch%E1%BA%A5p-T%C3%ADn/author-LcyqMNoBpNf6O7dZ2Ul1-Q">Triệu Chấp Tín</a>)<br></div>	</div>
